CALIFORNIA -- POLITICS; CALIFORNIA -- ELECTIONS; TELEVISION; DEBATES; POLITICAL 
CANDIDATES; CALIFORNIA GOVERNOR; VAN DE KAMP, JOHN K; FEINSTEIN, DIANNE; 
CALIFORNIA -- TAXES; ABORTION; ETHICS; FINANCIAL DISCLOSURE; POLITICAL 
CAMPAIGNS 
