Photo, Gordon Johnson, with his puppy, Rocky, at retirement party. He received 
the pet to keep him company on his travels. ; Photo, Stanley Alan Hershey, 
left, and Jan Vicki Fine, are being held in a Las Vegas jail in connection with 
Johnson's disappearance. 
</P>
